ADJNetWinCUR 
Base Table  WIS_NETWIN_EXTRACT_TMP 
Attribute Name  ADJNetWinCUR 
ColumnName  ADJNetWinCUR 
Logical Rolename   
RoleName   
Domain   
Physical Only  NO 
Definition  Adjusted net win for current revenue period: From bb_Revenue where Period_Id = 4, calculated as follows where B = bb_Revenue:


CASE
WHEN A.Lease_ID = 0 -- Fixed per Day
THEN ISNULL(( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills - (A.ProgPC * B.DaysOnLine)), 0)
WHEN A.Lease_ID = 1 -- Fixed per Month -- Added for TR012520
THEN ISNULL(( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills - (A.ProgPC * B.DaysOnLine)/30), 0)
WHEN A.Lease_ID = 2 -- % of Coin In
THEN ISNULL(( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills) - (B.ElecCoinIn * A.ProgPC/100), 0)
WHEN A.Lease_ID = 3 -- % of Gross Drop
THEN ISNULL(( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills) - ((B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn) * A.ProgPC/100), 0) -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
WHEN A.Lease_ID = 4 -- % of Net Win
THEN ISNULL(( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills) - (( B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills) * A.ProgPC/100), 0)
WHEN A.Lease_ID not in (0, 1, 2, 3, 4) or A.Lease_ID is NULL-- No Operator Pay
THEN ISNULL((B.ScaleDrop + B.ActualBillIn + B.ActualVoucherIn - B.ManualTicketOut - -- TR012520: ActualbillIn for ManualBillDrop, ActualVoucherIn for ManualTicketDrop
-- TR012520: Replaces b.Jackpots
( B.Jackpots + -- AttPaidJackpots
B.ActualAttPaidCC + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidExtBonus + -- As indicated
B.ActualAttPaidProg -- As indicated.
) -
B.Fills), 0)
END ADJNetWinCUR
